name: "Houses of the Holy" Led Zeppelin t-shirt
description:
Continuing with our type and music t-shirts series, we are happy to announce the new design!
"Houses of the Holy" is one of the most memorable songs of Led Zeppelin and this tee is celebrating that with a great phrase from it: "Let the Music be your Master."

This typography t-shirt is going to be available in grey. Wait soon for the pre sale!
